  npcName: Old Man
  npcPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d952a851392a84c4a8a1ed51430131fd, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - Come here young man....
  - Long have I watched this land, and long have I waited for someone like you
  - This world is not as simple as it seems. Creatures roam, trainers rise and fall,
    and only those with courage carve their path.
  - Take this moment, young one-this is where your journey begins.
  - But words alone mean little
  - A true trainer proves their worth in battle
  - Show me....do you have the strength to walk this path?
  - LET US DUAL!!
